Recently I started the Defiance Book Series. This Book Series has been on my list for a long time. A week ago I decided to start with it and it took me some time before I got into the story. After a while it became more exciting and I could no longer put the book down. I just finished reading the first book and I really enjoyed reading 2 different perspectives of the main characters and knowing how they think and feel about each other. I am excited about the next books. 

